08","chara":[{"id":302401,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"若菜纺","textCenter":"都已经开门30分钟了……"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":302401,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"阿见莉爱","textRight":"完全没有客人来啊……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302401,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"一、一会儿就会来了！"},{"chara":[{"id":302401}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"我昨晚也发了很多宣传！"},{"chara":[{"id":302401}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"我的粉丝应该都会来吧……"},{"chara":[{"id":302401,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"……[wait:1.0][chara:302401:cheek_0][chara:302401:face_mtn_ex_050.exp.json][chara:302401:lipSynch_1]啊！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"阿见莉爱","textRight":"怎么了？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302401}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"我才发现我发的宣传里有这些评论……"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"■评论（54）@熊太郎：北养实在是太远了啊@花子：抱歉，我没有空……@匿名：我去不了，还是你们去吧@西瓜君：能去就去","narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":150.0},{"chara":[{"id":302401,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"哈哈……也是啊！"},{"chara":[{"id":302401,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"说到底不是所有粉丝都会来捧场的嘛！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302401,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"（但是经过训练，@我已经是小有名气的评论家了……）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":302401,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"（总会有人过来的吧……）"},{"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"你好！","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302401,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"（来了！）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302401,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"若菜纺","textLeft":"欢迎光临！","turnEffect":"stop"},{"ch